data.description:
Are in need of a study break? Are your hungry? Well come out and enjoy some wings at Buffalo Wild Wings to support Jodaiko! In doing so you support us for our spring concert, Henka.

Our fundraiser is from 9 pm to 1 am, right after Tomo No Kai's Day of Remembrance! Tomo No Kai's Day of Remembrance starts are 7:30 pm, It's free and I hear there are gonna be some awesome performances. If you guys can you guys should definitely go to that and then to our fundraiser!

Please make sure to bring a flyer that is in the post below. If not, we'll have a couple ready at the door when you arrive. We'd really appreciate your support! 

Thanks to Bryan Le for the event picture!
data.name: Jodaiko Buffalo Wild Wings Fundraiser!

data.description:
When: 
February 19th: Kickoff Event/ Web AppJam Begins 
February 19th - February 26th: Competition
February 26th: Judging and Awards Ceremony  @ 6pm at Doheney Beach A

to SIGN UP: www.tinyurl.com/icsscWebJam

WebJam is a weeklong team competition where teams of students will create a fully functional web application. The app must utilize an API from at least one popular social or sharing website, and will utilize deployment platforms such as Heroku, AWS, or AppEngine.

Tired of passing up job openings that require HTML/CSS, Javascript, JQuery, node.js, ruby, python, asp.net, php, jsp or other web technologies? This competition will give you the opportunity to learn any of these and give you the ability to make your own websites!

Be sure to come out to Kick Off event February 19th at 6:00 pm where the theme will revealed and teams will be formed!

more information: http://student-council.ics.uci.edu/webjam/
data.name: ICSSC: Web AppJam

data.description:
Show some love at the Rotaract booth on Ring Road this Thursday in honor of Valentine's Day!

Rotaract will have a photo booth set up with props where you can take a photo with your significant others or friends, and just embrace the spirit of love and happy relationships. There will also be Valentine's Day grams for you to buy and give to the people you love and care about.

Photos will be taken with a DSLR camera and will be posted on our Facebook friend page for you to download (https://www.facebook.com/Rotaractclubofuci).

Prices:
$1 per photo
$1-1.50 per Valentine's Day Gram
data.name: Valentine's Day Photo Booth | Rotaract of UCI

data.description:
Come out and celebrate Lunar New Years with Konnect!

We'll be playing YUT NORI!

What is Yut Nori??

Yut Nori is  is a traditional board game played in Korea, especially during Korean New Year. It has even been used in fortune-telling, although this is not practiced anymore.

SO COME OUT AND PLAY!

When: Wednesday, February 13, 7pm
Where: Dr. White Room, Cross Cultural Center
